@startuml
title 嵌入式网通设备 Bug 分析 Agent - 本地运行部署图

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodeStyle rectangle

node "开发机器\n/home/sdmc/AgentProject" as Host {
  artifact ".env" as Env
  node "Python 虚拟环境\n.venv/" as Venv {
    component "FastAPI / Uvicorn\n127.0.0.1:9000" as API
    component "Streamlit\n127.0.0.1:8501" as UI
    component "评估脚本\nscripts/evaluate.py" as Eval
  }

  database "本地数据" as Data {
    folder "data/docs" as Docs
    folder "data/bugs" as Bugs
    folder "data/codebase" as Code
    folder ".chroma" as Chroma
  }
}

cloud "OpenAI 兼容 LLM 网关\nLLM_BASE_URL" as Gateway

UI --> API : BUG_AGENT_API_URL
API --> Gateway : LLM_BASE_URL\nLLM_API_KEY\nLLM_MODEL
Eval --> Gateway : 使用 --load-env 且 LLM_ENABLED=true 时
API --> Data : 文档 / Bug / 代码
Eval --> Data : eval_cases.json
Env --> API : 启动前由 shell 加载
Env --> UI : 超时时间 + API 地址
Env --> Eval : --load-env

@enduml
